<plot>After having a fight in a bar with a bunch of gunmen, the owner of a gold mine runs away with his children to an old cabin in the desert. The gang chases them to the cabin, and besiege the family inside, until the ammunition runs out. Unfortunately, the father dies, leaving his daughter, Anita (Carmelita Gonzalez)and his little son, Luis (Dagoberto Rodríguez), with the tough duty of protect the property title. After an unsuccessful attempt from the gunmen of steel the title, stopped by Charro Negro (Raúl De Anda), the gang will start a long chase behind the kids and Charro, in order to take them the paper.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?169751</url></doc>
